Package com.fluidops.iwb.mapping

Simple mapping framework.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
AlignmentOperator interface that helps providers to either generate owl:sameAs or align URIs before entering data into the triplestore the API is inspired by the SILK Link specification language: http://www4.wiwiss.fu-berlin.de/bizer/silk/spec/ It usually defines 2 datasources: source: the IWB repository target: the provider graph passed on as a List of Statements LinkCondition: currently simplified to a Pair of predicate URIs.
 

Class Summary
Align helper methods to align mapped resources to resources existing in the current DB
Bean jsp bean used for the mapping UI prototype.
Data base class for all mapping data models such as tree, table, graph, pojos, etc.
GraphData simple graph data model. does not know about RDF data model yet.
PojoData pojo datamodel.
PredicateAlignmentOperator  
RdfData RDF data model.
StringData raw string data
TableData table datamodel. delegates to com.fluidops.iwb.provider.TableProvider.Table
TreeData XML Tree data model
 

Enum Summary
TableData.PropertyType Column types for the underlying table, used when translating to RDF
 

Package com.fluidops.iwb.mapping Description

Simple mapping framework. Can assemble a pipeline which converts inputs to RDF. Intermediate formats can be trees, tables, pojos, graphs
